@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ezvief(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.61)) / (0.29 + (v1 + 0.38 * v2 + 0.27)))
    v2 = ((tmp * wp.abs(v1 + 0.73)) / (wp.cos(v1 + 0.31) / 0.71))
    v0 = (wp.abs(v1) + ((tmp + 0.04 + tmp + 0.08) + tmp))
    v0 = (wp.exp(v0) - wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.59)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.02) - (v2 + 0.05 + v0 + 0.82)) - wp.exp(tmp))
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
